{"title":"Detailed Miniature &#8220;Sculptures of Urban Decay&#8221;","link":"https://kottke.org/24/09/detailed-miniature-sculptures-of-urban-decay","date":1725632103000,"content":"\n        <p><img src=\"/cdn-cgi/image/format=auto,fit=scale-down,width=1200,metadata=none/plus/misc/images/j-smith-mini-01.jpg\" srcset=\"/cdn-cgi/image/format=auto,fit=scale-down,width=500,metadata=none/plus/misc/images/j-smith-mini-01.jpg 500w, /cdn-cgi/image/format=auto,fit=scale-down,width=1200,metadata=none/plus/misc/images/j-smith-mini-01.jpg 1200w\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1250\" height=\"1250\" alt=\"a miniature of a mah-jong supply store\" /></p>\n\n<p><img src=\"/cdn-cgi/image/format=auto,fit=scale-down,width=1200,metadata=none/plus/misc/images/j-smith-mini-02.jpg\" srcset=\"/cdn-cgi/image/format=auto,fit=scale-down,width=500,metadata=none/plus/misc/images/j-smith-mini-02.jpg 500w, /cdn-cgi/image/format=auto,fit=scale-down,width=1200,metadata=none/plus/misc/images/j-smith-mini-02.jpg 1200w\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1250\" height=\"1250\" alt=\"a miniature of a restaurant called Sushi Noodle Guy\" /></p>\n\n<p><img src=\"/cdn-cgi/image/format=auto,fit=scale-down,width=1200,metadata=none/plus/misc/images/j-smith-mini-03.jpg\" srcset=\"/cdn-cgi/image/format=auto,fit=scale-down,width=500,metadata=none/plus/misc/images/j-smith-mini-03.jpg 500w, /cdn-cgi/image/format=auto,fit=scale-down,width=1200,metadata=none/plus/misc/images/j-smith-mini-03.jpg 1200w\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1250\" height=\"1250\" alt=\"a miniature of a dumpster in front of a fence\" /></p>\n\n<p><img src=\"/cdn-cgi/image/format=auto,fit=scale-down,width=1200,metadata=none/plus/misc/images/j-smith-mini-04.jpg\" srcset=\"/cdn-cgi/image/format=auto,fit=scale-down,width=500,metadata=none/plus/misc/images/j-smith-mini-04.jpg 500w, /cdn-cgi/image/format=auto,fit=scale-down,width=1200,metadata=none/plus/misc/images/j-smith-mini-04.jpg 1200w\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1250\" height=\"1251\" alt=\"a miniature of a dumpster with a hand reaching down to grab it\" /></p>\n\n<p>Australian artist <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/joshua_smith_street_artist/\">Joshua Smith</a> makes extremely detailed and realistic miniatures of grimy, graffitied buildings — he calls them “sculptures of Urban Decay”.</p>\n\n<p>See also <a href=\"https://kottke.org/23/09/gritty-miniatures-of-classic-nyc-street-objects\">Gritty Miniatures of Classic NYC Street Objects</a>.</p>\n\n        \n\n         <p><strong>Tags:</strong> <a href=\"https://kottke.org/tag/art\">art</a> · <a href=\"https://kottke.org/tag/Joshua%20Smith\">Joshua Smith</a></p>\n\n         <p>💬 <a href=\"https://kottke.org/24/09/detailed-miniature-sculptures-of-urban-decay\">Join the discussion on kottke.org</a> →</p>\n\n    ","author":"Jason Kottke","siteTitle":"Kottke","siteHash":"89a883271b4598f9b33ebe87be70d38557bcd266e68aee521a8f93622e0ab723","entryHash":"0a082be721cdd6b7164bbd11ad33d6ea0c2df86096ba3ce090548d2cb72c3388","category":"Sites"}